Nevada: 10.7% Private QHP increase in 2nd half of January
Thu, 02/06/2014 - 1:59pm
Nevada keeps things short & to the point, as usual:
Update as of 2/1: 22,597 confirmed Qualified Plan Selections, 14,999 have paid. 27.1% of paid enrollees are under age 35.
 Nevada Health Link (@NVHealthLink) February 6, 2014
These numbers compare with 13,159 paid and 7,240 unpaid as of January 18th (20,399 total), a 10.7% increase in the past 2 weeks.
